cosineInVisionMod.name: cosineInVisionMod
cosineInVisionMod.contactinfo: Lianghwa Jou Cosine Communications Co. 1200 Bridge Parkway Redwood City, CA 94065 US 650-637-4777 ljou@cosinecom.com
cosineInVisionMod.description: The MIB module to describe generic objects for InVision system.

csInVisionServerName.name: csInVisionServerName
csInVisionServerName.description: A it is passed as argument to the trap csInVisionServerDown signifies that SMS Server is Down.

csInVisionBladeTable.name: csInVisionBladeTable
csInVisionBladeTable.description: A list of Blades which belongs to InVision database.

csInVisionBladeEntry.name: csInVisionBladeEntry
csInVisionBladeEntry.description: An entry containing management information applicable to a particular Blade.

csInVisionBladeSlotLocation.name: csInVisionBladeSlotLocation
csInVisionBladeSlotLocation.description: Slot Location of the Blade in the InVision database.

csInVisionBladeDescr.name: csInVisionBladeDescr
csInVisionBladeDescr.description: A textual string containing information about the blade. This string should include the name of the manufacturer and the product name.

csInVisionBladeType.name: csInVisionBladeType
csInVisionBladeType.description: The type of blade inserted in this slot.

csInVisionBladeState.name: csInVisionBladeState
csInVisionBladeState.description: The current state of this blade.

csInVisionBladeEnginesNumb.name: csInVisionBladeEnginesNumb
csInVisionBladeEnginesNumb.description: The number of engines on the blade.

csInVisionBladePortNumb.name: csInVisionBladePortNumb
csInVisionBladePortNumb.description: The number of ports on this blade (note, process blades have no ports).

csInVisionBladeSerialNumb.name: csInVisionBladeSerialNumb
csInVisionBladeSerialNumb.description: The serial number of the blade. This is a series of alphanumeric characters which uniquely identifies this blade.

csInVisionBladeHwVer.name: csInVisionBladeHwVer
csInVisionBladeHwVer.description: A textual string containing information about the hardware revision version.

csInVisionBladeSwVer.name: csInVisionBladeSwVer
csInVisionBladeSwVer.description: A textual string containing information about the software revision version.

csInVisionBladeReset.name: csInVisionBladeReset
csInVisionBladeReset.description: The software reset for this blade. It is an action object such that when set to 'reset' will reset this blade. Setting it to 'none' has no effect, and when it is retrieved the value will always be 'none' .

csInVisionBladeResyncedInInVision.name: csInVisionBladeResyncedInInVision
csInVisionBladeResyncedInInVision.description: A csInVisionBladeResyncedInInVision Inform PDU signifies that a blade had been resynced successfully.

csInVisionBladeInconsistentInInVision.name: csInVisionBladeInconsistentInInVision
csInVisionBladeInconsistentInInVision.description: A csgBladeInconsistent Inform PDU signifies that type of blade in InVision is different from type of blade type in device in same slot.

csInVisionBladeRestoreOnDevice.name: csInVisionBladeRestoreOnDevice
csInVisionBladeRestoreOnDevice.description: A csInVisionBladeResyncedInInVision Inform PDU signifies that a blade had been resynced successfully.

csInVisionVRRestoreSuccess.name: csInVisionVRRestoreSuccess
csInVisionVRRestoreSuccess.description: A csgVRRestoreSuccess Inform PDU signifies that InVision is succedded in restoring affecred VRs to device.

csInVisionVRRestoreFail.name: csInVisionVRRestoreFail
csInVisionVRRestoreFail.description: A csgVRRestoreFail Inform PDU signifies that InVision is failed in restoring affecred VRs to device.

csInVisionDeviceVRRestoreFail.name: csInVisionDeviceVRRestoreFail
csInVisionDeviceVRRestoreFail.description: A csInVisionDeviceVRRestoreFail Inform PDU signifies that Device is failed in restoring affecred VRs.

csInVisionFailToRegisterForTrap.name: csInVisionFailToRegisterForTrap
csInVisionFailToRegisterForTrap.description: A csInVisionFailToRegisterForTrap Inform PDU signifies that SMS Trap Server failed to register for trap with device.

csInVisionServerDown.name: csInVisionServerDown
csInVisionServerDown.description: A csInVisionServerDown Inform PDU signifies that SMS Server is Down. This trap is generated from launcher to any third party alarm display system.

csInVisionFailToUnRegisterForTrap.name: csInVisionFailToUnRegisterForTrap
csInVisionFailToUnRegisterForTrap.description: A csInVisionFailToUnRegisterForTrap Inform PDU signifies that SMS Trap Server failed to unregister for trap with device.
